WEBVTT

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Account exec: Thanks everyone for joining the Acme expansion kickoff. We're targeting a $1.2M ARR expansion to close by Friday.

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:58.000
Acme procurement: To be clear, all EU customer data must remain resident in EU data centers. This is a hard contractual requirement for us, not a preference.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:35.000
Engineering: Understood. Our current default storage region is US, so we'll need to confirm EU-only storage before go-live.

00:21:40.000 --> 00:22:05.000
Account exec: Great. We'll reflect the data residency commitment in the statement of work and circle back on the required owners.
